caption: The absolute best chicken sandwich of all time. Everything on the menu is good—I love the california salad, waffle fries, and the crispy chicken sando of course. One of the best things about this place is that the sandwich stays crispy through the delivery time and beyond. And—the salads are huge and in containers big enough to shake around all the dressing. Total dream
This chicken sandwich is insanely good. Can't believe the word hasn't gotten out yet.
